<p>The following is a comprehensive <b>list of policies and guidelines</b>. For descriptive directories see <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:List_of_policies" title="Wikipedia:List of policies">Wikipedia:List of policies</a>, <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:List_of_guidelines" title="Wikipedia:List of guidelines">Wikipedia:List of guidelines</a> and <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Manual_of_Style/Contents" title="Wikipedia:Manual of Style/Contents">Wikipedia:Manual of Style/Contents</a>.</p>
