<td><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:What_Wikipedia_is_not" title="Wikipedia:What Wikipedia is not">Wikipedia is an encyclopedia</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding:5px"><a href="/wiki/File:Scale_icon_green.svg" class="image"><img alt="Scale icon green.svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/79/Scale_icon_green.svg/47px-Scale_icon_green.svg.png" width="47" height="47" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/79/Scale_icon_green.svg/71px-Scale_icon_green.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/79/Scale_icon_green.svg/94px-Scale_icon_green.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="551" data-file-height="551" /></a></td>
