<div style="margin-top:2em; margin-bottom:2em;"></div>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="List">List</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedia:List_of_policies_and_guidelines&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: List">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<dl>
<dd>
<dl>
<dd><big><b>Large-print links</b></big> are broad, fundamental policies and guidelines that apply throughout Wikipedia.</dd>
<dd><b>Normal-print links</b> are policies and guidelines that are general in scope but may apply to more specific situations.</dd>
<dd><small><b>Small-print links</b></small> are policies and guidelines that are specific to a subject area or process on Wikipedia.</dd>
</dl>
</dd>
</dl>
