<dl>
<dt>Tutorials</dt>
</dl>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Help:Introduction_to_policies_and_guidelines" class="mw-redirect" title="Help:Introduction to policies and guidelines">Introduction to policies and guidelines</a>&#160;– a quick introduction to the major policies and guidelines for very new users.</li>
